title: A Vaccine Injury Class Action Started by a GP from the Whitsundays Advocating for her Injured Patients has Engaged a Barrister
cleaned_text:
A Vaccine Injury Class Action Started by a GP from the Whitsundays Advocating for her Injured Patients has Engaged a Barrister

A vaccine injury class action started by a GP from the Whitsundays advocating for her injured patients has engaged a barrister.

Though the class action started in Queensland, it is open to anyone in Australia.

 It now has over 100 litigants/ applicants who are bravely coming together to tell their stories of injuries and to join the action for justice and compensation for all injured. The action is set to filed in the new year, with the coming weeks being very busy in preparations. The support for this brings acknowledgment and hope to the injured, many of whom have been very isolated and alone for months.

The truth will be heard!

In love and courage

 Frontline Workers Speak Out!

A vaccine injury class action started by a GP from the Whitsundays advocating for her injured patients has engaged a barrister. Though the class action started in Queensland, it is open to anyone in Australia.

It now has over 100 litigants/ applicants who are bravely coming together to tell their stories of injuries and to join the action for justice and compensation for all injured. The action is set to filed in the new year, with the coming weeks being very busy in preparations. The support for this brings acknowledgment and hope to the injured, many of whom have been very isolated and alone for months. The truth will be heard!

No mainstream media at this stage.
